(define/contract (beautiful-substrings s k)
  (-> string? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let ([len (string-length s)])
    (define (vowel? c)
      (member c '(#\a #\e #\i #\o #\u)))
    (define (count-beautiful i j vowels consonants)
      (cond [(= j len) 0]
            [else
             (let* ([c (string-ref s j)]
                    [new-vowels (if (vowel? c) (+ vowels 1) vowels)]
                    [new-consonants (if (vowel? c) consonants (+ consonants 1))]
                    [beautiful (if (and (= new-vowels new-consonants) 
                                        (= 0 (modulo (* new-vowels new-consonants) k)))
                                   1
                                   0)])
               (+ beautiful
                  (count-beautiful i (+ j 1) new-vowels new-consonants)))]))
    (define (loop i total)
      (if (= i len) 
          total
          (loop (+ i 1) (+ total (count-beautiful i i 0 0)))))
    (loop 0 0)))
